        main.garden
            
            header.skies 
                h1 Neonpastel
                span#time

            section.grass
                article#intro 
                    :markdown-it
                        Hi, I hope you're doing well <3

                        There'll be links and stuff here in the future!
                        To other projects I'm working on, sites I think are neat

                        And resources I've used

                        Oh, you can at already find the repo for this website [on GitHub](https://github.com/Denperidge/neonpastel.net)

                        Have a nice day!
                

                +music 

                div.background

                br

            footer 
                each plant in plants
                    img(src=plant class="plant")

        script(src="index/utils.js")
